    {
      "id": "795062f1_3b94b0d7",
      "file_path": "docs/templating_functions.rst",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 187,
      "message": "mariadb-galera is not the best example as we use templates to access those secrets in other components that are not yet using the common secret template.\nI think that better example is in review for dgbuilder:\nsecrets:\n  - uid: 'db-root-password'\n    type: password\n    externalSecret: '{{ tpl (default \"\" .Values.config.db.rootPasswordExternalSecret) . }}'\n    password: '{{ .Values.config.dbRootPassword }}'\n  - uid: 'db-user-creds'\n    type: basicAuth\n    externalSecret: '{{ tpl (default \"\" .Values.config.db.userCredentialsExternalSecret) . }}'\n    login: '{{ .Values.config.db.userName }}'\n    password: '{{ .Values.config.dbSdnctlPassword }}'",
      "author": {
